data.description: Welcome to this fantastic home and opportunity to buy this home. The home is nestled on a large Cul de sac with easy access to main streets, shopping and schools. Wonderful two story home with high ceilings, Three bedrooms with two and a half bath plus a loft. Owners suite is downstairs and owners bathroom with separate tub and shower. Pretty kitchen with white cabinets and Corian counter tops. Freshly painted August 2023, newly installed lighting and bath fixtures in 2023. Carpets installed August 2023. Refrigerated A/C fully landscaped backyard with large shed.
